14:17.183 --> 14:20.020
YOU WANT TO HAVE MONEY,

14:20.020 --> 14:23.056
AND YOU WANT TO BE
A GOOD MOTHER TO THIS CHILD

14:23.056 --> 14:25.391
THAT YOU'RE CARRYING.

14:25.391 --> 14:26.927
YOU DON'T WANT TO DIE.

14:26.927 --> 14:29.229
‐DO NOT TOUCH ME AGAIN.
‐YES.

14:29.229 --> 14:30.597
I SAID, "STOP IT!"

14:30.597 --> 14:31.665
SHUT UP!

14:31.665 --> 14:34.267
[ MACHINE BEEPING FASTER ]

14:34.267 --> 14:36.670
[ INDISTINCT P. A. ANNOUNCEMENT ]

14:36.670 --> 14:39.706
♪♪♪♪

14:42.142 --> 14:45.946
NOW, YOU LISTEN TO ME.

14:45.946 --> 14:49.415
YOU DON'T WANT TO DIE.

14:49.415 --> 14:51.217
YOU'RE BEING DRAMATIC.

14:51.217 --> 14:52.686
YOU'RE SITTING
THERE RIGHT NOW

14:52.686 --> 14:55.355
BECAUSE YOU WANT ATTENTION,

14:55.355 --> 15:00.460
AND YOU WANT SOMETHING THAT I
AM NOT CAPABLE OF GIVING YOU.

15:00.460 --> 15:02.969
YOU WANT SYMPATHY.

15:02.969 --> 15:05.205
LIFE IS HARD.

15:05.205 --> 15:06.907
...IT HAPPENS.

15:06.907 --> 15:09.976
SO WHAT?
ANOTHER OLD NEGRO DIED.

15:12.846 --> 15:16.149
YOU MOVE ON.

15:16.149 --> 15:18.218
YOU DON'T WANT TO DIE.

15:18.218 --> 15:20.320
MNH‐MNH.

15:20.320 --> 15:23.256
IF YOU REALLY
WANTED TO DIE,

15:23.256 --> 15:26.660
[CHUCKLES] YOU WOULD HAVE
BURIED THAT RAZOR

15:26.660 --> 15:34.467
DEEP IN YOUR WRIST
AND SLIDE.

15:34.467 --> 15:37.070
I MEAN, IF YOU'RE GONNA DO IT,
YOU BETTER DO IT RIGHT.

15:37.070 --> 15:39.606
HMM?

15:42.709 --> 15:44.310
I OUGHT TO SLAP
YOUR ASS AGAIN

15:44.310 --> 15:50.483
FOR RUINING MY SHEETS
AND MY NIGHT.

15:50.483 --> 15:52.452
[ SNIFFLES ]

15:52.452 --> 15:55.989
I WAS TIRED.

15:55.989 --> 15:58.191
I HAVE TO GET
MY BEAUTY REST.

15:58.191 --> 16:01.234
♪♪♪♪

16:02.669 --> 16:03.837
I HAVE TO GO TO COURT,

16:03.837 --> 16:08.675
BUT I WAS HERE
FOR HOURS WITH YOU,

16:08.675 --> 16:11.845
YOU OF ALL PEOPLE.

16:11.845 --> 16:14.881
♪♪♪♪

16:16.650 --> 16:21.054
THE ONLY THING
KEEPING YOU ALIVE

16:24.558 --> 16:28.962
IS THAT BABY.

16:28.962 --> 16:32.465
YOU TAKE CARE OF HIM,

16:32.465 --> 16:36.469
AND I WILL
TAKE CARE OF YOU.

16:36.469 --> 16:39.439
I'LL MAKE SURE YOU EAT,

16:39.439 --> 16:43.710
EVEN IF IT'S JUST
THE CRUMBS FROM HIS TABLE.

16:47.480 --> 16:52.452
BUT IF YOU DON'T
TAKE CARE OF HIM,

16:52.452 --> 16:56.089
THEN DEATH WON'T BE
YOUR PROBLEM.

16:56.089 --> 16:58.725
IF YOU DO THAT AGAIN,

16:58.725 --> 17:01.034
I WILL MAKE SURE
YOU SURVIVE

17:01.034 --> 17:04.004
IN A CATATONIC STATE

17:04.004 --> 17:06.172
WHERE YOU KNOW EVERYTHING
GOING ON AROUND YOU,

17:06.172 --> 17:07.974
BUT YOU CAN'T MOVE.

17:07.974 --> 17:09.943
[ BEEPING CONTINUES ]

17:11.912 --> 17:15.849
MELISSA, I WILL SHOW YOU
WHAT IT'S LIKE

17:15.849 --> 17:23.489
TO BE LIVING
AND YET DEAD IN HELL.

17:25.491 --> 17:28.529
DO YOU HEAR ME?

17:28.529 --> 17:30.731
BECAUSE I WANT
TO BE REALLY SURE

17:30.731 --> 17:32.799
THAT YOU UNDERSTAND ME.

17:32.799 --> 17:35.836
♪♪♪♪

17:37.971 --> 17:40.707
IF YOU EVER,

17:40.707 --> 17:47.948
EVER DO ANYTHING
LIKE THIS AGAIN, HMM,

17:47.948 --> 17:51.518
WE WON'T HAVE TO COME
TO THE HOSPITAL,

17:51.518 --> 17:52.853
MNH‐MNH.

17:52.853 --> 17:55.556
BECAUSE I'LL THROW
YOUR ASS OFF A ROOF.

17:59.693 --> 18:01.535
[ SNIFFLES ]

18:03.970 --> 18:08.542
I'LL BE SURE
AND REVIVE YOU, THOUGH.

18:08.542 --> 18:11.077
DO YOU UNDERSTAND ME?

18:14.280 --> 18:15.982
I ASKED YOU A QUESTION.

18:15.982 --> 18:19.019
♪♪♪♪

18:21.454 --> 18:23.489
VERY GOOD.

18:23.489 --> 18:26.527
♪♪♪♪

18:34.668 --> 18:37.270
[ DOOR OPENS ]

18:37.270 --> 18:40.306
♪♪♪♪

18:40.306 --> 18:42.509
WELL,
DO YOU LIKE THIS ONE?

18:44.645 --> 18:47.514
ANNA?

18:47.514 --> 18:50.283
I GUESS IT'S FINE.

18:50.283 --> 18:53.053
AND WE'LL TAKE THAT ONE.

18:53.053 --> 18:54.655
HOW MUCH IS IT?

18:54.655 --> 18:56.222
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

18:56.222 --> 18:59.492
WELL, I HAVE TO PAY.

18:59.492 --> 19:01.334
I SAID,
"DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT."

19:01.334 --> 19:03.670
I'LL COVER IT.

19:03.670 --> 19:05.872
WE'LL TAKE THAT ONE.

19:05.872 --> 19:09.510
‐ARE YOU SURE?
‐YES.

19:09.510 --> 19:11.111
OKAY.

19:11.111 --> 19:14.915
OKAY. WE CAN GET
YOUR GRANDSON THIS MORNING.

19:14.915 --> 19:18.619
WHEN WOULD YOU LIKE
TO HAVE HIS FUNERAL?

19:18.619 --> 19:21.688
SATURDAY.

19:21.688 --> 19:23.824
THAT'S ENOUGH TIME.

19:23.824 --> 19:26.026
OKAY.

19:26.026 --> 19:29.129
I KNOW THIS IS
A VERY HARD TIME FOR YOU.

19:29.129 --> 19:31.464
YOU ARE IN MY PRAYERS.

19:31.464 --> 19:34.167
OKAY.

19:34.167 --> 19:35.836
I'LL SHOW YOU OUT.

19:35.836 --> 19:38.872
♪♪♪♪

19:46.780 --> 19:50.316
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS, RINGS ]

19:50.316 --> 19:52.352
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

19:56.422 --> 19:58.491
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

19:58.491 --> 19:59.960
MISS YOUNG.

19:59.960 --> 20:02.302
‐WHO IS THIS?
‐it's Mitch again.

20:02.302 --> 20:04.905
MITCH, WHERE IS BENNY?

20:04.905 --> 20:07.273
HE'S AWAY FROM THE PHONE.

20:07.273 --> 20:10.744
I KNOW THAT.
WHERE IS HE?

20:10.744 --> 20:13.146
HE JUST WENT OUT.

20:13.146 --> 20:14.915
YOU SAID THAT
THE LAST TIME I CALLED,

20:14.915 --> 20:18.585
AND HE HASN'T CALLED ME BACK.
NOW WHERE IS HE, MITCHELL?

20:18.585 --> 20:20.420
HE ‐‐ HE JUST RAN
TO THE STORE.

20:20.420 --> 20:22.789
WHERE IS HE?

20:22.789 --> 20:24.157
HE JUST WENT OUT.

20:24.157 --> 20:25.926
Mitch, are you lying?

20:25.926 --> 20:27.594
OH, LORD. HE DIDN'T
GO OUT TO WAR NOW.

20:27.594 --> 20:28.829
DID HE, MITCHELL?

20:28.829 --> 20:30.330
No.

20:30.330 --> 20:32.065
THEN WHERE IS HE?

20:32.065 --> 20:35.235
♪♪♪♪

20:35.235 --> 20:37.170
‐MISS YOUNG.
‐Mitchell,

20:37.170 --> 20:40.306
I ASKED YOU A QUESTION.

20:40.306 --> 20:41.775
LOOK.

20:41.775 --> 20:44.778
BENNY ASKED ME
NOT TO TELL YOU.

20:44.778 --> 20:47.147
MITCHELL, I'M NOT IN THE MOOD
FOR THIS RIGHT NOW.

20:47.147 --> 20:49.750
WHERE IS BENNY?

20:49.750 --> 20:51.985
WHERE IS HE?

20:51.985 --> 20:53.787
WHAT'S GOING ON?

20:53.787 --> 20:55.421
HE WON'T TELL ME
WHERE BENNY IS.

20:55.421 --> 20:57.323
‐WHO IS IT?
‐IT'S MITCHELL, HIS FRIEND.

20:57.323 --> 21:00.934
GIVE ME THE PHONE.

21:00.934 --> 21:03.103
HELLO?
‐YEAH. WHO'S THIS?

21:03.103 --> 21:04.370
This is Katheryn Cryer.

21:04.370 --> 21:06.106
NOW HANNA HAS BEEN
THROUGH ENOUGH RIGHT NOW.

21:06.106 --> 21:07.373
SHE NEEDS TO SPEAK TO BENNY.

21:07.373 --> 21:08.875
MS. CRYER, HE ‐‐
HE'S IN JAIL,

21:08.875 --> 21:10.944
And, uh, he asked me
not to tell her.

21:10.944 --> 21:12.245
FOR WHAT?

21:12.245 --> 21:14.414
HE GOT ARRESTED
FOR THAT QUINCY MAXWELL THING.

21:14.414 --> 21:16.149
[ SIGHS ] OKAY.

21:16.149 --> 21:17.518
LOOK. DON'T TELL HER.
ALL RIGHT?

21:17.518 --> 21:20.687
SHE'LL FREAK OUT.
‐AH, YOU'RE RIGHT.

21:20.687 --> 21:22.288
Is there anything
you can do for him?

21:22.288 --> 21:24.658
YEAH. IT'S...
I ‐‐ I'LL MAKE A CALL.

21:24.658 --> 21:26.392
‐WHERE IS HE?
‐HE'S FINE.

21:26.392 --> 21:28.294
LOOK.
JUST DON'T TELL HER.

21:28.294 --> 21:29.830
YOUNG MAN,
YOU LET ME HANDLE THIS.

21:29.830 --> 21:31.464
NOW TAKE DOWN MY NUMBER.
‐WHERE IS BENNY?

21:31.464 --> 21:32.699
IS HE ALL RIGHT?

21:32.699 --> 21:34.668
HE'S FINE.

21:34.668 --> 21:36.436
OH, OKAY.
I'LL CALL YOU IN A FEW.

21:36.436 --> 21:37.604
OKAY.

21:37.604 --> 21:38.772
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

21:38.772 --> 21:40.541
[ SIGHS ]

21:40.541 --> 21:42.743
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

21:42.743 --> 21:43.877
I'M GOING TO FIND BENNY.

21:43.877 --> 21:45.145
HE'S FINE.

21:45.145 --> 21:47.013
SOMETHING IS GOING ON
THAT HE'S NOT TELLING ME.

21:47.013 --> 21:48.314
NO. HANNA, HE IS FINE.

21:48.314 --> 21:49.716
THEN WHY ISN'T HE
CALLING ME BACK?

21:49.716 --> 21:51.518
WHY ISN'T HE TALKING TO ME?
‐HE ‐‐ HE'S JUST BEEN OUT?

21:51.518 --> 21:53.520
‐THEN WHERE?
‐HE'S FINE. HE'S OKAY.

21:53.520 --> 21:55.155
YOU KNOW WHERE HE IS.
WHY WON'T YOU TELL ME?

21:55.155 --> 21:56.790
‐BECAUSE HE'S...
‐KATHERYN, WHERE IS HE?

21:56.790 --> 21:59.993
‐HE'LL CALL WHEN HE'S...
‐WHERE IS HE?

21:59.993 --> 22:01.835
HE'S IN JAIL, HANNA.

22:04.004 --> 22:06.206
‐WHAT?
‐HE IS.

22:06.206 --> 22:08.509
WHAT?

22:08.509 --> 22:10.544
QUINCY MAXWELL'S DEATH.

22:10.544 --> 22:13.580
♪♪♪♪

22:14.815 --> 22:16.583
I'M CALLING.
I'M COMING.

22:16.583 --> 22:19.152
I'M CALLING SOMEONE.

22:19.152 --> 22:20.486
I'M NOT PLAYING.

22:26.793 --> 22:29.062
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

22:30.230 --> 22:31.998
HEY.

22:33.366 --> 22:35.902
[ SIGHS ] DAMN.

22:35.902 --> 22:37.838
WHAT?

22:37.838 --> 22:39.472
I WAS ASLEEP A LONG TIME.

22:39.472 --> 22:41.207
YEAH.

22:41.207 --> 22:43.176
[ GROANS ]

22:43.176 --> 22:44.845
OH, HOW LONG?

22:44.845 --> 22:47.313
A LONG TIME.

22:47.313 --> 22:48.682
DAMN.

22:48.682 --> 22:50.651
HOW DO YOU FEEL?

22:50.651 --> 22:53.587
HMM?

22:53.587 --> 22:54.688
I'M FINE.

22:54.688 --> 22:55.856
GOOD.

22:55.856 --> 22:57.991
[ GRUNTS ]

22:59.726 --> 23:01.101
I WANT TO GO HOME.
‐YEAH.

23:01.101 --> 23:02.903
THE DOCTOR SAID
HE'S GONNA DISCHARGE YOU

23:02.903 --> 23:05.105
WHENEVER YOU WAKE UP.

23:05.105 --> 23:08.341
AND THEY ARE VERY HAPPY
WITH YOUR PROGRESS.

23:08.341 --> 23:09.776
HMM?

23:09.776 --> 23:11.077
OKAY. GOOD.

23:11.077 --> 23:14.247
OKAY. WELL, I'M GONNA GET
THE CAR AND COME BACK.

23:14.247 --> 23:15.248
YEAH?
‐OKAY.

23:15.248 --> 23:16.850
YOU DID GOOD. MM‐HMM.

23:16.850 --> 23:19.753
AND BY THE WAY, YOUR CLOTHES
IS RIGHT THERE IN THE BAG.

23:19.753 --> 23:23.423
YEAH?
‐OKAY. THANKS.

23:23.423 --> 23:25.258
I'M GONNA GET THE CAR.

23:25.258 --> 23:26.693
OKAY.

23:28.995 --> 23:30.697
[ DOOR OPENS ]

23:30.697 --> 23:33.734
♪♪♪♪

23:35.769 --> 23:37.738
[ GROANS ]

23:37.738 --> 23:41.374
♪♪♪♪

23:41.374 --> 23:43.544
WYATT.

23:46.279 --> 23:48.715
DAD.

23:48.715 --> 23:50.584
HOW YOU FEELING, SON?

23:52.919 --> 23:55.055
I'M FINE.

23:55.055 --> 23:58.324
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

23:58.324 --> 24:01.668
WELL, MY SON'S
IN THE HOSPITAL.

24:01.668 --> 24:03.403
I WANTED TO COME BY
AND SEE HIM.

24:06.206 --> 24:10.210
‐WELL, I DON'T WANT TO SEE YOU.
‐COME ON. WHAT'S THE MATTER?

24:10.210 --> 24:13.680
YOU DON'T HAVE ANY TIME
FOR YOUR OLD MAN, HUH?

24:13.680 --> 24:16.082
NO, NONE.

24:16.082 --> 24:18.218
WYATT, LET...

24:19.686 --> 24:22.689
ARE YOU AFRAID OF ME, SON?

24:22.689 --> 24:24.791
NO.

24:24.791 --> 24:29.229
THEN WHY THE HELL DID YOU
JUST BACK AWAY FROM ME, WYATT?

24:29.229 --> 24:31.765
I DON'T KNOW, DAD.

24:31.765 --> 24:34.300
MAYBE IT'S BECAUSE YOU THREW ME
IN A CELL WITH SOME MANIAC,

24:34.300 --> 24:37.538
MAYBE BECAUSE YOU THREW ME
ON THE GROUND, BEAT ME.

24:37.538 --> 24:40.440
NO. I'M NOT AFRAID OF YOU.

24:40.440 --> 24:42.375
I'M JUST GONNA
SIT HERE AND TAKE IT.

24:42.375 --> 24:45.478
YOU KNOW SOMETHING, WYATT CRYER?
I AM STILL YOUR FATHER.

24:45.478 --> 24:48.849
YOU CAN'T TALK
TO ME THAT WAY.

24:48.849 --> 24:51.985
THAT DOESN'T GIVE YOU THE RIGHT
TO DO WHAT YOU WANT TO ME.

24:51.985 --> 24:54.588
NO, IT DOESN'T.

24:54.588 --> 24:56.222
I'M NOT HAVING IT.

24:56.222 --> 24:59.492
I DON'T HAVE
TO TAKE IT ANYMORE...

24:59.492 --> 25:01.968
OKAY. FINE.

25:01.968 --> 25:03.403
...BECAUSE I HAVE ENOUGH MONEY
TO NEVER HAVE TO DEAL

25:03.403 --> 25:04.905
WITH YOUR...AGAIN.

25:07.908 --> 25:09.743
YES, YOU DO.
YOU HAVE YOUR INHERITANCE.

25:09.743 --> 25:12.045
YEP, ALL OF IT.

25:12.045 --> 25:15.081
♪♪♪♪

25:16.316 --> 25:22.188
SO YOU CAN JUST
FORGET ABOUT ME.

25:22.188 --> 25:24.257
I CAN'T FORGET ABOUT YOU,
WYATT.

25:24.257 --> 25:27.661
YOU'RE MY SON.
I LOVE YOU.

25:27.661 --> 25:31.765
[ CHUCKLES ]

25:31.765 --> 25:33.199
[ LAUGHS ]

25:33.199 --> 25:34.868
WHAT'S SO DAMN FUNNY,
WYATT?

25:34.868 --> 25:36.136
‐YOU LOVE ME?
‐YES.

25:36.136 --> 25:38.839
‐WHOA.
‐I LOVE YOU.

25:38.839 --> 25:41.808
DEAL WITH IT.

25:41.808 --> 25:45.145
NOTHING YOU SAY IS GONNA
KEEP ME FROM TESTIFYING.

25:45.145 --> 25:46.880
OKAY?

25:46.880 --> 25:48.348
OH, REALLY?

25:48.348 --> 25:51.484
YOU THINK THAT'S WHY
I CAME DOWN HERE,

25:51.484 --> 25:55.088
BECAUSE I'M AFRAID THAT YOU'RE
GONNA TESTIFY AGAINST ME?

25:55.088 --> 25:58.291
‐YEAH, I DO.
‐WYATT, I DON'T GIVE A RAT'S ASS

25:58.291 --> 26:01.127
ABOUT YOU
TESTIFYING AGAINST ME.

26:01.127 --> 26:05.872
WHAT I CARE ABOUT IS THAT
I COULDN'T GET TO YOU, OKAY?

26:05.872 --> 26:08.041
YOU WERE GONE, AND I COULDN'T
EVEN LOOK FOR YOU

26:08.041 --> 26:09.342
BECAUSE I WAS IN JAIL.

26:09.342 --> 26:11.211
HMM.

26:11.211 --> 26:13.714
I KNOW.

26:13.714 --> 26:16.449
I PUT YOU THERE.

26:16.449 --> 26:18.985
JUST HOW THE HELL DO YOU THINK
THAT MAKES ME FEEL?

26:18.985 --> 26:23.590
I ‐‐ I DON'T GIVE A DAMN
HOW IT MAKES YOU FEEL.

26:26.326 --> 26:28.061
OKAY.

26:31.297 --> 26:34.635
OKAY, I KNOW THAT YOU PUT THE
MONEY IN AN OFFSHORE ACCOUNT.

26:34.635 --> 26:38.004
HERE'S WHAT I WOULD
LIKE YOU TO DO.

26:38.004 --> 26:40.106
GIVE IT BACK
TO YOUR MOTHER AND I

26:40.106 --> 26:43.276
SO THAT WE CAN MAKE SURE
THAT YOU ARE OKAY.

26:43.276 --> 26:45.011
MM.

26:45.011 --> 26:47.614
HMM.

26:47.614 --> 26:49.349
SO YOU CAN CONTROL ME.

26:49.349 --> 26:51.284
‐NO.
‐MM.

26:51.284 --> 26:52.853
WYATT, WE DON'T WANT
TO CONTROL YOU.

26:52.853 --> 26:54.521
WHAT WE WANT TO DO,
WE'LL PUT YOUR MONEY

26:54.521 --> 26:56.823
IN AN ACCOUNT SO YOUR BILLS
WILL GET PAID.

26:56.823 --> 26:58.024
YOUR MOTHER WILL
INVEST IT FOR YOU.

26:58.024 --> 27:00.133
WE'LL GIVE YOU
AN ALLOWANCE EVERY MONTH.

27:03.236 --> 27:06.472
WHY THE HELL WOULD
I DO THAT, HUH?

27:08.742 --> 27:10.110
I'M NOT GONNA HURT YOU,
BUT YOU NEED TO HEAR

27:10.110 --> 27:11.712
WHAT I'M SAYING RIGHT NOW.

27:11.712 --> 27:16.750
YOU HAVE A SUBSTANCE‐ABUSE
PROBLEM, WYATT.

27:16.750 --> 27:18.318
I'M GETTING TREATMENT.

27:18.318 --> 27:19.452
YEAH.
I KNOW, AND I'M SO ‐‐

27:19.452 --> 27:22.756
I'M SO PROUD OF YOU
FOR THAT.

27:22.756 --> 27:24.357
I AM,
BUT YOU LISTEN TO ME.

27:24.357 --> 27:25.759
YOUR MOTHER
INVESTING THE MONEY

27:25.759 --> 27:30.163
WOULD BE A VERY GOOD IDEA,
VERY GOOD.

27:30.163 --> 27:32.465
YEAH. I'M JUST ‐‐
I'M NOT GONNA DO A DAMN THING.

27:32.465 --> 27:34.034
OKAY?

27:34.034 --> 27:35.536
WYATT, PLE ‐‐ PLEASE.

27:35.536 --> 27:38.038
JUST WOULD YOU LISTEN
TO WHAT I'M SAYING?

27:38.038 --> 27:39.139
‐DON'T.
‐PLEASE, WYATT.

27:39.139 --> 27:42.042
DON'T "WYATT, PLEASE" ME.
I'M SICK OF IT.

27:42.042 --> 27:45.646
OKAY? I'M SICK OF YOU.

27:45.646 --> 27:46.847
ALL RIGHT?

27:46.847 --> 27:49.282
I DON'T WANT TO SEE YOU
OR MOM AGAIN.

27:49.282 --> 27:51.351
OKAY?
AND YOU'RE GONNA GO AWAY.

27:51.351 --> 27:52.318
AND THIS TIME,
IT'S GONNA BE FOR LIFE.

27:52.318 --> 27:54.420
LOOK AT ME.
LOOK AT ME.

27:54.420 --> 27:57.958
I'M BEGGING YOU.
I AM BEGGING YOU.

27:57.958 --> 27:59.726
PLEASE, WYATT,
DON'T DO THIS.

27:59.726 --> 28:01.334
‐I'M TESTIFYING.
‐TESTIFY.

28:01.334 --> 28:03.904
PLEASE DO.
I'M TALKING ABOUT THE MONEY.

28:03.904 --> 28:05.506
IT'S NOT ABOUT ME.
‐IT'S DONE!

28:05.506 --> 28:06.640
IT'S ABOUT YOUR MOTHER.
IT'S ABOUT YOU.

28:06.640 --> 28:09.475
IT IS DONE, OKAY?
IT'S DONE.

28:09.475 --> 28:11.912
IT IS ALL DONE.

28:11.912 --> 28:14.748
ALL RIGHT?
LEAVE ME ALONE.

28:14.748 --> 28:17.884
I NEVER WANT
TO SEE YOU AGAIN.

28:17.884 --> 28:19.052
ALL RIGHT?

28:19.052 --> 28:20.687
BYE.

28:22.823 --> 28:25.859
♪♪♪♪

28:30.330 --> 28:33.299
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS, DIALS ]

28:33.299 --> 28:37.704
‐Yes?
‐OSCAR, IT'S JIM CRYER.

28:37.704 --> 28:38.905
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

28:38.905 --> 28:41.207
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

28:41.207 --> 28:43.143
I'M TRYING
TO LOCATE WARWICK.

28:43.143 --> 28:44.778
I NEED TO KNOW EXACTLY
WHAT YOU HAVE IN PLACE

28:44.778 --> 28:46.112
TO GET THE MONEY
BACK FROM MY SON,

28:46.112 --> 28:48.014
AND I NEED TO KNOW IT
RIGHT NOW.

28:48.014 --> 28:51.518
THAT'S ALREADY IN MOTION.

28:51.518 --> 28:55.789
YES, BUT I NEED
TO KNOW WHAT IT IS.

28:55.789 --> 28:58.925
It's best you don't know.

28:58.925 --> 29:01.902
YOU LISTEN TO ME, OSCAR.

29:01.902 --> 29:06.372
MY SON IS DOING EVERYTHING
HE CAN TO RECOVER FROM THIS,

29:06.372 --> 29:07.808
TO GET ON THE OTHER
SIDE OF THIS,

29:07.808 --> 29:10.043
BUT HE'S DONE IT BEFORE,
AND IT WILL NOT WORK.

29:10.043 --> 29:13.413
HE WILL FAIL.

29:13.413 --> 29:17.283
SO I NEED YOU TO GET
THE MONEY BACK FROM WYATT

29:17.283 --> 29:20.053
BEFORE HE GOES OFF
THE DEEP END.

29:20.053 --> 29:22.589
CAN YOU DO THAT
FOR ME, PLEASE?

29:22.589 --> 29:24.324
LOOK. I KNOW YOU DON'T
KNOW ME, MR. CRYER,

29:24.324 --> 29:25.892
BUT I'M REALLY GOOD
AT WHAT I DO.

29:25.892 --> 29:28.494
WELL, I DON'T HAVE ANY PROOF
OF THAT YET, DO I, OSCAR?

29:28.494 --> 29:30.731
I GOT YOU BACK MILLIONS
FROM CANDACE NOW, DIDN'T I?

29:30.731 --> 29:32.332
IN MY BUSINESS,
YOU'RE ONLY AS GOOD

29:32.332 --> 29:34.367
AS YOUR LAST ELECTION.

29:34.367 --> 29:35.936
I'M ON IT.

29:37.904 --> 29:39.439
THANK YOU.

29:39.439 --> 29:40.541
And you find Warwick.

29:40.541 --> 29:42.008
IF YOU DON'T MIND,
I HAVE TO GO.

29:42.008 --> 29:43.009
HI.
‐HI.

29:43.009 --> 29:46.212
‐IT'S ME, OSCAR.
‐UH, DO I KNOW YOU?

29:46.212 --> 29:48.782
NO, BUT I WANT TO TALK
TO YOU ABOUT AN OFFER.

29:56.256 --> 29:59.159
♪♪♪♪

30:03.269 --> 30:06.339
‐BENJAMIN?
‐YEAH.

30:06.339 --> 30:07.774
YEAH.

30:10.476 --> 30:13.279
YOU WANT "HI"?
IS THAT BETTER?

30:13.279 --> 30:14.981
ALL RIGHT.

30:14.981 --> 30:18.018
DON'T ACT
SO HAPPY TO SEE ME.

30:18.018 --> 30:20.787
LOOK. I DON'T KNOW WHAT
THE HELL IS GOING ON HERE.

30:20.787 --> 30:22.723
WELL, I DO.

30:22.723 --> 30:24.658
‐WHAT?
‐QUINCY MAXWELL.

30:24.658 --> 30:26.560
I'M NOT
TALKING ABOUT THAT.

30:26.560 --> 30:29.195
I'M TALKING ABOUT
THE SECRET SERVICE.

30:29.195 --> 30:30.263
‐WHAT?
‐YEAH.

30:30.263 --> 30:32.365
THE DAMN SECRET SERVICE
WAS IN HERE.

30:32.365 --> 30:33.466
THEY WERE THREATENING ME,

30:33.466 --> 30:35.802
ASKING ME ALL KIND
OF CRAZY QUESTIONS.

30:35.802 --> 30:37.838
THERE'S NOTHING HERE
ABOUT A SECRET SERVICE.

30:37.838 --> 30:39.305
WELL, I'M TELLING YOU.
THEY WERE HERE.

30:39.305 --> 30:42.342
WELL, IF THEY WERE HERE,
IT WOULD BE IN THE REPORT.

30:42.342 --> 30:44.578
LOOK. THEY WERE HERE.

30:44.578 --> 30:47.080
THEY CAME IN HERE,
TOLD ME I WAS FREE TO GO.

30:47.080 --> 30:48.849
THEY LEFT.
THEY CAME BACK IN HERE

30:48.849 --> 30:50.316
AND STARTED SAYING
A BUNCH OF CRAZY STUFF

30:50.316 --> 30:54.555
ABOUT TERRORISTS AND TOLD ME
TO WAIT RIGHT HERE.

30:54.555 --> 30:56.523
‐THAT'S ODD.
‐THAT'S ODD, YEAH.

30:56.523 --> 30:58.525
NO KIDDING.

30:58.525 --> 31:00.093
I'LL LOOK INTO THAT
WHEN I LEAVE HERE.

31:00.093 --> 31:02.402
[ SIGHS ]

31:02.402 --> 31:04.037
SO WHAT?
YOU'RE MY LAWYER NOW?

31:05.539 --> 31:07.040
ALL RIGHT.
WELL, TELL ME WHY I'M HERE.

31:07.040 --> 31:08.842
WHY AM I HERE?
‐YOU'RE HERE BECAUSE

31:08.842 --> 31:11.645
THEY HAVE CHARGED YOU
WITH MURDER.

31:11.645 --> 31:15.749
‐WHAT?
‐YES.

31:15.749 --> 31:18.885
OH, MY GOD.

31:18.885 --> 31:21.688
IT'S JUST CRAZY.
THIS IS CRAZY.

31:21.688 --> 31:26.359
THEY ‐‐ THEY LITERALLY JUST
TOLD ME I WAS FREE TO GO.

31:26.359 --> 31:27.928
I'LL TELL YOU THIS.

31:27.928 --> 31:31.932
NONE OF WHAT'S GOING ON HERE
MAKES ANY LEGAL SENSE.

31:31.932 --> 31:35.168
I'VE BEEN WAITING FOR A
FORMAL RESPONSE TO CHARGES.

31:35.168 --> 31:39.105
AND WHEN I ASK THEM,
THEY SAY THEY'RE WORKING ON IT.

31:39.105 --> 31:41.374
SO I CAN WALK OUT OF HERE.

31:41.374 --> 31:43.577
TECHNICALLY, YES.

31:43.577 --> 31:46.246
WELL, LET'S GO.

31:46.246 --> 31:48.481
MNH‐MNH.

31:48.481 --> 31:50.651
I ‐‐ I'M CONFUSED.

31:50.651 --> 31:53.954
YEAH. ME, TOO.

31:53.954 --> 31:56.322
WHO COULD BE
DOING THIS TO YOU?

31:56.322 --> 31:57.290
DOING WHAT?
WHAT THE HELL DO YOU MEAN?

31:57.290 --> 31:59.860
THIS RAILROADING.

31:59.860 --> 32:02.803
I DON'T KNOW.

32:02.803 --> 32:05.338
OKAY. LISTEN TO ME.

32:05.338 --> 32:07.107
THIS MAKES NO SENSE.
OKAY?

32:07.107 --> 32:08.709
YOU HAVE A CHARGE PENDING.

32:08.709 --> 32:10.210
THEY'RE HOLDING YOU HERE.

32:10.210 --> 32:12.012
AND NOW YOU'RE TELLING ME
THE SECRET SERVICE

32:12.012 --> 32:15.181
HAS BEEN HERE
ASKING YOU QUESTIONS?

32:15.181 --> 32:17.584
WHAT IS THAT ABOUT, BENJAMIN?
‐OKAY. OKAY. ALL RIGHT.

32:17.584 --> 32:20.721
WHAT?

32:20.721 --> 32:23.023
SO YOU'RE DOING THIS.

32:23.023 --> 32:24.124
WHAT?

32:24.124 --> 32:25.526
YOU'RE DOING THIS.

32:25.526 --> 32:26.593
[ SCOFFS ]

32:26.593 --> 32:28.962
LOOK. I CAN PULL OFF
SOME THINGS,

32:28.962 --> 32:30.430
BUT THIS IS EVEN
BIGGER THAN THAT.

32:30.430 --> 32:33.634
COME ON. VERONICA,
WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME?

32:33.634 --> 32:35.969
HUH?

32:35.969 --> 32:38.539
I KNOW I PUT IT ON YOU,
OKAY,

32:38.539 --> 32:40.941
BUT THIS IS CRAZY.

32:40.941 --> 32:42.843
YOU'RE TELLING ME
YOU WANT ME THAT BAD

32:42.843 --> 32:45.546
THAT YOU PLAY
THESE GAMES WITH ME?

32:45.546 --> 32:47.914
THIS IS MY LIFE HERE.
YOU PLAY THESE GAMES WITH ME?

32:51.284 --> 32:55.321
I ASSURE YOU, LITTLE BOY.

32:55.321 --> 32:57.958
I AM NOT PLAYING
ANY GAMES WITH YOU.

32:57.958 --> 33:00.761
THIS IS SERIOUS.

33:00.761 --> 33:02.002
SO THIS ISN'T
YOU DOING THIS?

33:02.002 --> 33:03.937
NO.

33:06.607 --> 33:07.808
WELL,
THEN WHO THE HELL IS?

33:07.808 --> 33:08.942
THAT'S WHY ASKED YOU

33:08.942 --> 33:10.944
WHAT HIGH‐POWERED PERSON
YOU PISSED OFF!

33:10.944 --> 33:12.879
NOBODY BESIDES YOU.

33:12.879 --> 33:14.314
I'M HIGH‐POWERED, YES.

33:14.314 --> 33:17.150
BUT THIS IS ON A WHOLE
NOTHER LEVEL, BENJAMIN.

33:19.720 --> 33:21.387
IT'S PROBABLY YOUR HUSBAND.

33:21.387 --> 33:23.056
‐DAVID CAN'T REACH THIS HIGH.
‐YEAH.

33:23.056 --> 33:25.491
WELL, IT SURE IN THE HELL
LOOKS LIKE IT TO ME.

33:25.491 --> 33:28.529
♪♪♪♪

33:29.896 --> 33:32.232
‐I'LL GET YOU OUT OF HERE.
‐YEAH.

33:32.232 --> 33:33.233
WHEN?

33:33.233 --> 33:34.935
SOON.

33:37.137 --> 33:38.304
ALL RIGHT.
WELL, IN THE MEANTIME,

33:38.304 --> 33:39.573
I NEED TO TALK TO MY MOM.

33:39.573 --> 33:40.607
YOU WILL.

33:40.607 --> 33:42.576
WELL, I CAN'T
CALL HER FROM HERE.

33:42.576 --> 33:45.478
SHE'LL KNOW.
‐I CAN'T DO ANYTHING ABOUT THAT.

33:45.478 --> 33:47.013
WELL,
LET ME USE YOUR PHONE?

33:47.013 --> 33:48.849
‐YOU CAN'T DO THAT IN HERE.
‐DAMMIT, VERONICA.

33:48.849 --> 33:51.184
I NEED TO KNOW WHAT
IN THE HELL IS GOING ON.

33:51.184 --> 33:53.820
AS I SAID,
I WILL LOOK INTO IT.

33:56.790 --> 33:59.325
THEN FINE.

33:59.325 --> 34:03.303
FINE.

34:03.303 --> 34:08.374
YOU KNOW, THAT'S WHERE YOU
WOULD INSERT A "THANK YOU."

34:08.374 --> 34:10.443
[ CHUCKLES ]

34:10.443 --> 34:12.045
WOW.

34:12.045 --> 34:16.349
UH, THANK YOU,
VERONICA.

34:16.349 --> 34:18.585
‐AND BENJAMIN?
‐WHAT?

34:18.585 --> 34:19.953
WE WILL DEAL
WITH THE ISSUE

34:19.953 --> 34:23.389
OF WHO PUT IT ON WHOM

34:23.389 --> 34:26.326
WHEN I GET YOU
OUT OF HERE.

34:26.326 --> 34:30.764
AND THEN YOU WILL HAVE
TO WORK OFF THIS RETAINER.

34:30.764 --> 34:33.800
♪♪♪♪

34:36.903 --> 34:40.841
I'LL BE IN TOUCH.

34:40.841 --> 34:42.609
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

34:42.609 --> 34:45.646
♪♪♪♪

34:52.619 --> 34:55.255
♪♪♪♪

34:55.255 --> 34:57.357
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

34:57.357 --> 34:58.859
[ TELEPHONE BEEPS ]
HELLO?

34:58.859 --> 35:00.093
Hey, it's Anna.

35:00.093 --> 35:03.469
‐HI.
‐He's going home.

35:03.469 --> 35:04.638
OKAY. GREAT.

35:04.638 --> 35:06.540
Okay.
I'll keep you posted.

35:06.540 --> 35:09.510
THANKS.

35:09.510 --> 35:10.944
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

35:10.944 --> 35:12.646
[ TELEPHONE BEEPS ]

35:12.646 --> 35:15.682
♪♪♪♪

35:16.249 --> 35:17.618
HEY.

35:17.618 --> 35:20.020
HOW YOU'D KNOW
I WAS HERE?

35:20.020 --> 35:21.087
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

35:21.087 --> 35:22.255
‐I WAS ‐‐
‐ARE YOU FOLLOWING ME?

35:22.255 --> 35:24.224
‐NO. JUSTIN...
‐WHAT

35:24.224 --> 35:25.425
...I JUST NEEDED
TO TALK TO YOU.

35:25.425 --> 35:27.360
‐WELL, YOU CAN'T.
‐IT'S IMPORTANT.

35:27.360 --> 35:28.562
THEN YOU
SHOULD HAVE CALLED.

35:28.562 --> 35:30.030
‐I CAN'T.
‐WHY?

35:30.030 --> 35:31.431
YOUR MOM.

35:31.431 --> 35:33.333
WHAT ABOUT MY MOM?

35:33.333 --> 35:36.570
SHE'S THREATENED TO TELL MY WIFE
IF I DON'T LEAVE YOU ALONE.

35:36.570 --> 35:37.671
‐WHAT?
‐YEAH.

35:37.671 --> 35:38.905
THAT'S WHY I HAD
TO FOLLOW YOU HERE,

35:38.905 --> 35:40.040
AND I COULDN'T CALL.

35:40.040 --> 35:41.141
I HAD TO MAKE SURE
SHE'S NOT AROUND

35:41.141 --> 35:43.844
AND DOESN'T
HAVE YOUR PHONE.

35:43.844 --> 35:46.112
ALL RIGHT. WELL, YOU SHOULDN'T
BE FOLLOWING ME.

35:46.112 --> 35:48.549
‐I'M SORRY.
‐I DON'T LIKE THAT.

35:48.549 --> 35:49.449
WHAT DID YOU
WANT ME TO DO?

35:49.449 --> 35:52.218
JUST DON'T DO THAT AGAIN.

35:52.218 --> 35:55.589
OKAY. I STILL HAVE
TO ASK YOU SOMETHING.

35:55.589 --> 35:57.090
WHAT?

35:57.090 --> 35:59.192
‐WILL SHE DO IT?
‐OF COURSE, SHE WILL.

35:59.192 --> 36:01.067
JEFFREY, YOU'RE NOT
JUST SAYING THAT

36:01.067 --> 36:02.435
SO THAT
I LEAVE YOU ALONE?

36:02.435 --> 36:04.370
NO.

36:04.370 --> 36:07.407
♪♪♪♪

36:11.978 --> 36:14.280
LOOK. I KNOW YOU DON'T
WANT TO SEE ME AGAIN.

36:17.250 --> 36:20.621
THAT'S NOT TRUE.

36:20.621 --> 36:22.723
ARE YOU SURE?

36:22.723 --> 36:24.525
YEAH.

36:24.525 --> 36:27.561
♪♪♪♪

36:29.029 --> 36:34.300
JEFFREY, I SCREWED UP
WHEN I ATTACKED YOU.

36:34.300 --> 36:37.938
PLEASE, TELL ME.

36:37.938 --> 36:42.042
AM I DOING BETTER?

36:42.042 --> 36:45.411
TIME WILL TELL.

36:45.411 --> 36:47.113
TIME WILL TELL.

36:51.952 --> 36:52.886
LOOK. I ‐‐ I OPENED
MY HEART TO YOU,

36:52.886 --> 36:55.789
AND YOU DON'T EVEN CARE.

36:55.789 --> 36:57.290
DON'T DO THAT.

36:57.290 --> 36:58.291
DO WHAT?

36:58.291 --> 36:59.826
TURN IT AROUND ON ME.

36:59.826 --> 37:02.068
I DO CARE.

37:02.068 --> 37:05.572
WELL,
THEN HELP ME OUT HERE.

37:05.572 --> 37:06.973
HOW?

37:06.973 --> 37:08.542
GIVE ME A PASS ON THAT.

37:08.542 --> 37:11.945
A PASS?
YOU TRIED TO HURT ME.

37:11.945 --> 37:15.582
‐I KNOW.
‐AND I ALMOST GOT KILLED.

37:15.582 --> 37:19.319
I KNOW, AND I'M SORRY.

37:19.319 --> 37:20.787
[ CHUCKLES ]

37:20.787 --> 37:23.724
YOU SEE HOW SIMPLE
THAT SORRY SOUNDED?

37:26.226 --> 37:27.460
YEAH.
I'M ASHAMED OF IT, TOO.

37:27.460 --> 37:30.096
MM‐HMM.
CAN WE STOP THIS?

37:30.096 --> 37:31.297
I MEAN, I DON'T WANT
TO TALK ABOUT IT.

37:31.297 --> 37:32.633
NEITHER DO I.

37:32.633 --> 37:34.134
THEN STOP BRINGING IT UP.

37:34.134 --> 37:36.670
THEN STOP MAKING ME
FEEL BAD WHEN I DON'T.

37:38.772 --> 37:42.208
OKAY. UM, I THINK
YOU SHOULD JUST LEAVE.

37:42.208 --> 37:43.309
ALL RIGHT? I KIND OF WANT
TO BE BY MYSELF, OKAY?

37:43.309 --> 37:45.378
‐JEFFREY.
‐NO, NO, NO, NO.

37:45.378 --> 37:47.548
THIS ‐‐ THIS IS ‐‐
IS A LOT GOING ON.

37:47.548 --> 37:50.684
YOU'RE ‐‐ YOU'RE MARRIED.
‐DON'T DO THIS.

37:50.684 --> 37:53.419
LOOK. YOUR MOM IS THREATENING
TO TELL MY WIFE,

37:53.419 --> 37:55.355
AND I'M STILL HERE.

37:55.355 --> 37:59.159
IF THAT DOESN'T PROVE TO YOU
HOW COMMITTED I AM,

37:59.159 --> 38:00.967
I DON'T KNOW WHAT WILL.

38:00.967 --> 38:02.903
COMMITTED?
COMMITTED TO WHAT?

38:02.903 --> 38:04.605
YOU.

38:04.605 --> 38:07.073
OFFICER JUSTIN,
I BARELY KNOW YOU.

38:09.309 --> 38:11.678
I KNOW. BUT, YOU KNOW,
WE CAN GET TO KNOW EACH OTHER.

38:11.678 --> 38:14.047
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.
WHAT I NEED YOU TO DO

38:14.047 --> 38:17.417
IS TO RESPECT MY WISHES
AND TO RESPECT MY SPACE.

38:17.417 --> 38:21.187
I'M TRYING.

38:21.187 --> 38:23.724
BY FOLLOWING ME?

38:25.892 --> 38:28.128
OKAY.
I WANTED TO SEE YOU.

38:28.128 --> 38:30.396
YOU WANTED TO SEE ME?
WE WERE JUST TOGETHER!

38:30.396 --> 38:32.899
LIKE, WHEN WAS THAT?
‐AND THAT WAS TOO LONG AGO.

38:32.899 --> 38:35.636
WHAT? YOU ‐‐
YOU DON'T MISS ME?

38:35.636 --> 38:38.539
OKAY,
I REALLY NEED YOU TO GO

38:38.539 --> 38:42.408
AND JUST GIVE ME SOME SPACE
AND TIME TO CLEAR MY HEAD.

38:42.408 --> 38:45.278
♪♪♪♪

38:45.278 --> 38:47.648
OH, IS HE COMING OVER?

38:47.648 --> 38:51.317
‐WHO?
‐WYATT.

38:51.317 --> 38:53.820
ALL RIGHT.
YOU SHOULD GO.

38:53.820 --> 38:55.221
‐I'M SO‐‐ I'M SORRY.
‐IT'S FINE.

38:55.221 --> 38:56.122
JUST ‐‐ JUST GOOD
‐I'M SORRY.

38:56.122 --> 38:58.458
CAN YOU CALL ME, PLEASE?
‐YEAH.

39:00.527 --> 39:03.036
ALL RIGHT. BYE.

39:03.036 --> 39:06.072
♪♪♪♪

39:09.009 --> 39:10.744
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

39:13.279 --> 39:15.816
‐[ EXHALES ]
‐HI. [ CHUCKLES ]

39:15.816 --> 39:17.751
HELLO.

39:17.751 --> 39:19.820
I HAVEN'T HEARD
FROM YOU IN AWHILE.

39:19.820 --> 39:22.689
YEAH. WELL, I GOT
A BIT DISTRACTED.

39:22.689 --> 39:24.424
I APOLOGIZE.

39:24.424 --> 39:25.759
YEAH. NO, IT'S OKAY.

39:25.759 --> 39:27.127
YEAH.

39:27.127 --> 39:29.329
THANK YOU FOR INVITING ME
TO COFFEE.

39:29.329 --> 39:31.665
YEAH. WELL,
IT'S MY PLEASURE.

39:31.665 --> 39:33.600
MM.

39:33.600 --> 39:35.536
HOW ARE YOU?

39:35.536 --> 39:39.472
I'M OKAY.

39:39.472 --> 39:42.142
ME, TOO.

39:42.142 --> 39:46.046
I, UM, I JUST
WANT TO APOLOGIZE

39:46.046 --> 39:47.614
ABOUT THE OTHER NIGHT.

39:47.614 --> 39:49.282
OH, NO, NO.
THERE'S NO NEED FOR THAT.

39:49.282 --> 39:51.384
NO.
I HA‐‐ I HAVE TO.

39:51.384 --> 39:54.320
I WAS OVERWHELMED.

39:54.320 --> 39:55.589
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:55.589 --> 39:57.123
AS WAS I.

39:57.123 --> 39:59.359
YEAH.

39:59.359 --> 40:01.234
AND WE WERE BOTH,
UH...

40:01.234 --> 40:04.404
‐A BIT DRUNK.
‐OOH, JUST ‐‐ JUST A BIT.

40:04.404 --> 40:06.940
I WAS WAY
TOO AGGRESSIVE.

40:06.940 --> 40:08.141
NO. I MEAN, FOR SOME.

40:08.141 --> 40:10.677
NO, NO, NO. ADMIT IT.
IT WAS TOO MUCH.

40:10.677 --> 40:14.314
NO. IT WAS ACTUALLY EVERYTHING
I WANTED IT TO BE.

40:16.349 --> 40:19.452
ERICA.

40:19.452 --> 40:24.124
YOU'RE A MAN
OF VERY MANY TALENTS.

40:24.124 --> 40:26.627
THANK YOU.

40:26.627 --> 40:27.794
ARE YOU BLUSHING.

40:27.794 --> 40:29.630
NO. I AM N‐‐
I AM NOT BLUSHING.

40:29.630 --> 40:30.664
REALLY?
AND WHAT'S THAT?

40:30.664 --> 40:32.733
THIS IS SURPRISE.

40:34.234 --> 40:36.803
I REALLY DIDN'T THINK
YOU WANTED TO SEE ME AGAIN.

40:36.803 --> 40:39.472
NO, ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

40:39.472 --> 40:42.008
WELL, THANK YOU
FOR TELLING ME.

40:42.008 --> 40:45.245
OF COURSE.

40:45.245 --> 40:48.114
I REALLY LIKE YOU, DAVID.

40:48.114 --> 40:50.216
FEELING'S MUTUAL.

40:50.216 --> 40:53.219
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:53.219 --> 40:58.358
BUT, UM, I JUST
HAVE TO SAY THIS.

40:58.358 --> 41:01.401
I DON'T DO THE CRAZY
EX‐WIFE THING.

41:01.401 --> 41:03.036
I COMPLETELY UNDERSTAND.

41:03.036 --> 41:04.638
I MEAN, THE THING
WITH THE FLOWERS?

41:04.638 --> 41:06.172
I AM SO SORRY.

41:06.172 --> 41:08.274
YEAH. I MEAN, WHAT MORE
IS SHE CAPABLE OF?

41:08.274 --> 41:09.976
RIGHT?

41:09.976 --> 41:13.013
♪♪♪♪

41:17.784 --> 41:20.220
YOU HAVE NO IDEA.

41:20.220 --> 41:23.256
♪♪♪♪

