WHAT YOU'RE GOING TO DO.

41:47.881 --> 41:48.815
YOU'LL SEE.

41:48.815 --> 41:50.416
I THINK ABOUT YOU
ALL THE TIME,

41:50.416 --> 41:52.185
I MEAN, YOUR BODY, ASS.
MM, MM, MM.

41:52.185 --> 41:53.754
WAIT. YOU KNOW.
